casebody.data:
Court of Appeals.

Memorandum, of decisions in which no opinions were filed.

Filed April 15, 1890. Desda Reynolds, Resp’t, v. The Equitable Accident Ass’n of Binghamton, N. Y., App’lt. H. Greenfield, for resp’t; David Murray, for app’lt.

Judgment affirmed, with costs, on opinion below. All concur.

Affirming 17 N. Y. State Rep., 337.
